{"tid":204512,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪每個一開始睇三國演義既人都會覺得劉備好慘好可憐?","createTime":"2017-04-17T06:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T14:19:16.000Z","uid":67824,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fcc13a3743f0a33983cd68bc28b41ab5d758312","tid":204512,"uid":67824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"覺得佢好有理想, 好有大志, 蜀國係最高尚, 大好人一名, 永遠正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但大過先會慢慢發覺原來佢先係個故事入面最世界仔果個<br />\n<br />\n靠虛偽, 靠呃, 開口埋口都仁義道德, 要企係最高道德高地去批判其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾會認為佢唔抵可憐, 變左討厭佢"},{"pid":"a3ec3e7f155dc9057f92c637ebcf989cf33042ba","tid":204512,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:13:22.000Z","msg":"同老毛一樣 爛仔起家<br />\n其他人賣命 死 佢坐擁為王"},{"pid":"82d6d3a0e452957a34139d8813b0dc0626c9cafb","tid":204512,"uid":7892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:20:14.000Z","msg":"我細個既時候都會鐘意劉備<br />\n人愈就大發覺曹操既魅力"},{"pid":"f4237cac86d010b2b0aa2d301979697790c30324","tid":204512,"uid":67824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我細個既時候都會鐘意劉備<br />\n人愈就大發覺曹操既魅力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n硬係覺得佢果種好人過左火，變到有d假<br />\n<br />\n反而曹丞相似返個真人"},{"pid":"c2c1a0515e94d0c30e913a860b6e4ffb8ab53e51","tid":204512,"uid":67824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同老毛一樣 爛仔起家<br />\n其他人賣命 死 佢坐擁為王</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎住漢室個名行騙<br />\n<br />\n同啊毛拎馬列出黎一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c46eaeef2e8813419ed8ebf139f87218ccd79c","tid":204512,"uid":67824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a891ad5f1b5a46c512d5e553ca16181ae4bd9c9b","tid":204512,"uid":60856,"like":0,"di